{"tid":1287340,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（忽發奇想）自制敲擊樂","createTime":"2019-07-05T07:19:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T13:13:46.000Z","uid":228195,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"12180ba06f6805626bd370ba53f355d3bbf9ebb3","tid":1287340,"uid":228195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:19:09.000Z","msg":"早前見到有巴打用紙皮或者木板做手工藝<br />\n令我最近有個想法<br />\n同樣係用紙皮 再加 一層雙面膠紙 做drum set<br />\n<br />\n同樣地會用到紙皮，紙皮做鼓<br />\n我認為可以加上雙面膠紙黎改變音色<br />\n<br />\n包書膠其實好硬淨，容易入手<br />\n成碌木棍咁可以敲到發發聲<br />\n用作做鼓「棍」其實一流<br />\n<br />\n我想法係紙皮外面貼上一層雙面膠紙。膠紙除左保護紙皮鼓被打爛打穿，當用鼓棍大大力打落有雙面膠紙既鼓面時候，膠紙痴力會卸去部分敲擊力，<span style=\"color: red;\">影響鼓手抽起鼓棍作再做快速重複敲擊動作</span>。多作練習可訓練手劈、碗力同速度。<br />\n<br />\n雙面膠鼓缺點應該就係雙面膠痴力容易受到其他因素減弱，例如脫落、濕左。當然除左雙面膠之外，可能泥膠、粉團都對初學者練習有幫助。<br />\n<br />\n紙皮鼓十分方便，有利初學者帶住四圍去。拎上手都得。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nJcxRmo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnJcxRmo.gif&h=fed3976b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"965f1ebbda9f2defc00eabe538f508cef5e1b60f","tid":1287340,"uid":204352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:32:22.000Z","msg":"一齊加入樂團lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451b8e85e007f77435de80f8a220e30ea5e79359","tid":1287340,"uid":197540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T10:58:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ac4a09b83d7b40cf49052a97bf6f40bb708518","tid":1287340,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T11:14:38.000Z","msg":"又打鼓又做gym<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03905c227771ed55383955fa9aeb6a366cd1e7c3","tid":1287340,"uid":31778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:02:34.000Z","msg":"太長啲人唔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鼓佬here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c260c816da96ff7882758f138ab5d264cba445","tid":1287340,"uid":228195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"03905c227771ed55383955fa9aeb6a366cd1e7c3","tid":1287340,"uid":31778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:02:34.000Z","msg":"太長啲人唔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鼓佬here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:13:46.000Z","msg":"無緊要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得可行到需要時咪誠邀身邊人一齊敲擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n身邊有咩用具咪用咩嚟做樂器<br />\n有創意全部人都係鼓佬"}]}